#

Saffron Infused Lemon Garlic Shrimp Bisque

$18.5
320 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

SeafoodSoupGourmet

Description

A luxurious and aromatic bisque featuring succulent shrimp, infused with saffron and brightened with zesty lemon and garlic.

Ingredients

  • Fresh shrimp: 1 lb
  • Shallots: 2, finely chopped
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Saffron threads: 1/4 tsp
  • Chicken stock: 4 cups
  • Heavy cream: 1 cup
  • Fresh lemon juice: 2 tbsp
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Fresh parsley: 2 tbsp, chopped
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
